{"tid":1565231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"致 每一位香港的小孩子","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T02:25:18.000Z","uid":18648,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02c2410d5d4ec3b9861bc3df06b215ae5b95c2df","tid":1565231,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"香港的小孩子們<br />\n<br />\n你們生於這個充滿煙火的香港<br />\n<br />\n這個地方<br />\n沒有公義<br />\n沒有人權<br />\n只有荒謬<br />\n<br />\n哥哥知道數名十三歲的小孩<br />\n被困入兒童院<br />\n<br />\n哥哥眼見那兩名十四歲<br />\n滿身裝備的小孩走上前線<br />\n<br />\n哥哥認識那名十五歲<br />\n拿著鐵通的小孩與我並肩<br />\n<br />\n對不起<br />\n哥哥沒什麼能力保護你們<br />\n<br />\n那名十四歲但外表像小學生的你<br />\n還記得嗎？<br />\n你說你沒錢開飯<br />\n哥哥從銀包中拿出僅餘的一百元給你<br />\n想請你食個午餐<br />\n你說不要<br />\n你說為香港而捱餓<br />\n一切都值得<br />\n<br />\n一向再堅強的我<br />\n都禁不住除下眼罩<br />\n抹乾眼淚<br />\n<br />\n有次在街上看到那名幼稚園生<br />\n他的背包掛著一條白絲帶<br />\n<br />\n那天晚上<br />\n走到海旁<br />\n對天發誓<br />\n哥哥永遠也會保護你們<br />\n哥哥會為你爭取更好的香港<br />\n哥哥保證光複香港的責任不會要你們承擔<br />\n<br />\n哥哥求求你們<br />\n不要走到上前線<br />\n前線的責任留哥哥們<br />\n保護你們這些種子<br />\n讓你們平安地發芽<br />\n帶給香港新希望<br />\n<br />\n還在媽媽懷抱中的你<br />\n長大後希望你們知道<br />\n有班哥哥姐姐一直為香港奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n哥哥姐姐愛你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個成為了戰俘 <br />\n二十二歲的哥哥上"},{"pid":"d8bdd3d03295eb0cb6e658189d9254f1709ef4d4","tid":1565231,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:24:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=4d0b9f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"ae72898060df28207581e27ec1d21a6fa5241a15","tid":1565231,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ee35cf7651a6535a1b8fd6de30365d05aef7df","tid":1565231,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"072ce0d4ff68f6545bc798650f25e20211816ade","tid":1565231,"uid":314443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"好滾動"},{"pid":"bedcb3c5a3a124df82a15e99a9ad791dcc0f208f","tid":1565231,"uid":6020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":